:"**TypeScript support**: Fully typed with comprehensive prop interfaces"},"192":{"id":"/docs/components/icon-45","page_id":"/docs/components/icon","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/icon#features","content":"**Bento integration**: Extends Bento Icon with additional Antares-specific features"},"193":{"id":"/docs/components/icon-46","page_id":"/docs/components/icon","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/icon#props","content":"The `Icon` component accepts the following props:"},"194":{"id":"/docs/components/icon-47","page_id":"/docs/components/icon","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/icon#prop-inheritance","content":"The component extends `BentoIconProps` and passes through all standard HTML attributes and accessibility props to the underlying Bento Icon component. This includes:"},"195":{"id":"/docs/components/icon-48","page_id":"/docs/components/icon","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/icon#prop-inheritance","content":"**Accessibility**: `aria-label`, `aria-describedby`, `role`, `title`"},"196":{"id":"/docs/components/icon-49","page_id":"/docs/components/icon","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/icon#prop-inheritance","content":"**Events**: `onClick`, `onMouseOver`, `onFocus`, etc."},"197":{"id":"/docs/components/icon-50","page_id":"/docs/components/icon","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/icon#prop-inheritance","content":"**Styling**: `className`, `style`, `data-*` attributes"},"198":{"id":"/docs/components/icon-51","page_id":"/docs/components/icon","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/icon#prop-inheritance","content":"**Transform**: `rotate`, `flip` for icon transformations"},"199":{"id":"/docs/components/icon-52","page_id":"/docs/components/icon","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/icon#size-variants","content":"Specify explicit width and height values:"},"200":{"id":"/docs/components/icon-53","page_id":"/docs/components/icon","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/icon#size-variants","content":"You can use different values for width and height:"},"201":{"id":"/docs/components/icon-54","page_id":"/docs/components/icon","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/icon#slots","content":"The Icon component uses Bento's slot system with the following component hierarchy and available slot override points:"},"202":{"id":"/docs/components/icon-55","page_id":"/docs/components/icon","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/icon#available-slot-overrides","content":"**`icon`**: Overrides the entire BentoIcon component - affects icon loading, caching, sprite/SVG mode switching, data attributes, and the overall icon wrapper"},"203":{"id":"/docs/components/icon-56","page_id":"/docs/components/icon","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/icon#available-slot-overrides","content":"**`icon.content`**: Overrides the BentoIllustration component - affects SVG transformations (rotate, flip), accessibility attributes (`role`, `focusable`, `aria-labelledby`), viewBox calculations, and final SVG element rendering"},"204":{"id":"/docs/components/icon-57","page_id":"/docs/components/icon","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/icon#available-slot-overrides","content":"For complete slot override patterns and examples, see the `@bento/slots` package documentation."},"205":{"id":"/docs/components/icon-58","page_id":"/docs/components/icon","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/icon#custom-icons","content":"While the Icon component loads design system approved icons from the CDN by default, teams can introduce custom icons using the underlying Bento Icon system."},"206":{"id":"/docs/components/icon-59","page_id":"/docs/components/icon","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/icon#adding-icons-synchronously","content":"Use the `set` method to add custom icons that are available immediately:"},"207":{"id":"/docs/components/icon-60","page_id":"/docs/components/icon","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/comp